abstract: Buffalo Bills Coach Rex Ryan says running back LeSean McCoy will not play against Dallas Cowboys after McCoy missed second practice with knee injury; other pro football news.
lead_paragraph: Bills running back LeSean McCoy missed a second straight practice with a knee injury, and Coach Rex Ryan said his approach was that McCoy would not play against the Cowboys on Sunday.

headline.main: Ryan Says McCoy Will Not Play
headline.print_headline: Ryan Says McCoy Will Not Play
